-- Italy's Impregilo Awarded the Ruta del Sol Highway Concession in Colombia
-- Marco Bertacche
-- 2010-07-28T10:43:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-28/italy-s-impregilo-awarded-the-ruta-del-sol-highway-concession-in-colombia.html

          
          
             Impregilo SpA won the Ruta del Sol
concession in Colombia, according to a statement through the
Italian exchange today.  
 The total value of the concession is $3.7 billion, while
Impregilo will have a 40 percent share in the contract, the
statement said.  
          
          


  


        